<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/covid-19-may-increase-heat-extremes-this-summer/">COVID-19 May Increase Heat Extremes This Summer</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">The temporary respite from pollution due to economic shutdown could result in more extreme weather events.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/bruce-melton/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Bruce Melton</a></span>, </dd>
